item.title: CVE-2019-16203|2024-08-05T01:10:41.488Z -- brocade -- brocade%20fabric%20os
item.description: Brocade Fabric OS Versions before v8.2.2a and v8.2.1d could expose the credentials of the remote ESRS server when these credentials are given as a command line option when configuring the ESRS client.

item.title: CVE-2019-16204|2024-08-05T01:10:41.440Z -- brocade -- brocade%20fabric%20os
item.description: Brocade Fabric OS Versions before v7.4.2f, v8.2.2a, v8.1.2j and v8.2.1d could expose external passwords, common secrets or authentication keys used between the switch and an external server.
